  "description": "In `src/agent_takt/cli/commands/run.py`, move the `scheduler_cycle_started` event (currently emitted once before the loop, lines 114\u2013118) and the `scheduler_cycle_completed` event (currently emitted once after, lines 137\u2013143) so that each fires once per loop iteration, inside the loop. Add a `cycle_index` integer field to both event payloads. The `scheduler_cycle_started` event fires at the top of each iteration (before `run_once`); `scheduler_cycle_completed` fires after result accumulation (before the break check). The final CLI summary lines (cycle summary + final state + JSON dump) remain a single end-of-run report outside the loop.",
